1. *Telefonu* sam kupio pre tri dana. (I bought the phone three days ago.)
2. On uvek drži *telefonu* u ruci. (He always holds the phone in his hand.)
3. Nisam mogao da pronađem *telefonu*. (I could not find the phone.)
4. Ona je učinila nešto sa *telefonu*. (She did something with the phone.)
5. Prošli mesec sam kupio *telefonu*. (I bought the phone last month.)
6. Ljudi su se okupljali oko *telefona*. (People were gathering around the phone.)